skill.name: BU-GI AUTO BREACHER
skill.description: The BU-GI Drone is a soft-breaching device that can break through floors and barricades, soft walls that aren't reinforced.

skill.name: F-NATT DREAD MINE
skill.description: The F-NATT DREAD MINE is a throwable device that sticks to walls, so it can be hidden in places where fear can fester. Fenrir comes equipped with 5 mines and can activate 3 at a time anywhere on the map.

skill.name: KLUDGE DRONE
skill.description: Deployable drone that either takes control of electronic devices or destroys them after a short delay.

skill.name: SPEC-IO ELECTRO-SENSOR
skill.description: An augmented reality headset which detects and tags electronic devices. When activated, any electronic gadgets used by Attackers, including drones and phones, can be identified and pinged.

skill.name: KAWAN HIVE LAUNCHER
skill.description: Fires canisters which attach to any surface, and release a swarm of nano-bots. Any Defender which enters a swarm will not only be pinged, but the swarm will follow the affected Defender for a period, allowing Grim to track them in real time.

skill.name: R.O.U. PROJECTOR SYSTEM
skill.description: When thrown or sent rolling, the ROU drops a line of projectors behind it, which activate to create a wall of light obscuring the line of sight.

skill.name: KIBA BARRIER
skill.description: A modified kunai that sticks to a surface after it's thrown and releases a material that first expands then solidifies, creating a bulletproof barrier.

skill.name: RAZORBLOOM SHELL
skill.description: A proximity grenade that can be thrown and attached to any surface. When deployed, any Attacker that enters its radius will start the Razorbloom's timer, followed by a powerful explosion.

skill.name: TALON-8 CLEAR SHIELD
skill.description: A rectangular shield made of bulletproof, transparent material. Shield can be carried as means of selfdefence or deployed on floors, doorways and windows.

skill.name: KÓNA STATION
skill.description: An automated dispenser which shoots out healing shots, similar to Doc's Stim Pistol. Station targets any operator in its radius and heals 30 HP per charge.

skill.name: RCE-RATERO CHARGE
skill.description: An explosive drone device. Drone can be attached to surfaces before detonation. Works as a soft breach device.

skill.name: SURYA GATE
skill.description: When this device is launched onto a doorway, window hatch, or any kind of wall, it creates a laser grid which covers the entrance way, denying entry by the Attackers or destroying projectiles that try to pass through it.

skill.name: ARGUS LAUNCHER
skill.description: Launcher, which launches small cameras. These cameras can burrow into any surface, including reinforced walls and hatches, and provide a camera view on both sides of the deployed surface.

skill.name: S.E.L.M.A. AQUA BREACHER
skill.description: When thrown onto a breachable surface, the SELMA will extend a set of explosive arms, then detonate, creating a wide opening which can be used to establish line of sight.

skill.name: BANSHEE SONIC DEFENSE
skill.description: When deployed on a wall or floor, the Banshee will emit a low buzzing noise whenever an Attacker enters its radius and line of sight alerting Defenders as well as slowing the Attacker.

skill.name: REMAH DASH
skill.description: When activated, he performs a quick dash, making him move faster than any other Defender for a short period of time. Additionally using this ability allows to knock down players and breach soft walls or barricades. Without activating the ability, Oryx can jump up the open hatches.

skill.name: GEMINI REPLICATOR
skill.description: When activated, it creates a holographic decoy of Iana, which she can control remotely like a drone.

skill.name: MAG-NET SYSTEM
skill.description: A powerful electromagnet that intercepts and redirects projectiles towards itself, then detonates them.

skill.name: LV EXPLOSIVE LANCE
skill.description: These burrow into walls, even indestructible walls, pushing an explosive charge through the wall to the other side, and create an explosion on both sides of the wall. Primarily used as gadget-clearing device, as damage to players is minimal.

skill.name: GLANCE SMART GLASSES
skill.description: Special glasses that nullify the effects of Stun Grenades, Smoke Grenades, and other related gadgets.

skill.name: HEL PRESENCE REDUCTION
skill.description: A gadget that when activated, erases her image from cameras.

skill.name: VOLCÁN CANISTER
skill.description: Incendiary bomb that can be deployed on floors or walls and explodes when destroyed.

skill.name: GARRA HOOK
skill.description: Fires several grappling hooks then pulls Amaru towards the hooks. This allows Amaru to travel up hatches, second story or higher windows, or rooftops.

skill.name: PEST LAUNCHER
skill.description: A slingshot that launches small robots called Pests that can hack the Attacking team's drones (including Twitch's Shock Drones) and make them your own.

skill.name: TRAX STINGERS
skill.description: Devices that when deployed, unfold and spread in its proximity. They both slow down opponents and make noise when traversing across them, also damage opponents.

skill.name: AIRJAB LAUNCHER
skill.description: Repulsion grenades that will stick to any surface and knock down all in its effective radius when triggered.

skill.name: "RTILA" ELECTROCLAW
skill.description: Device can be thrown onto any surface it can attach to, electrifying metal objects within a certain radius of the gadget.

skill.name: CCE SHIELD
skill.description: When in use, shield fully extends to cover Clash's front-side. The Shield also has a taser function that can damage and slow down enemies in front of Clash.

skill.name: BREACHING TORCH
skill.description: It can make holes in any breachable surface, including Reinforced Walls, creating new lines of sight quietly.

skill.name: EVIL EYE
skill.description: This camera is bulletproof, gyroscopic and can see through smoke. It can shoot low-damage lasers at the expence of vulnerability. If laser overheats, camera automatically closes. Can be deployed on any solid surface.

skill.name: PRISMA
skill.description: Special devices that project volumetric displays of Alibi. If an enemy were to interfere with them, they will activate a tracking feature that will cause the victim to be detected for a short while.

skill.name: EE-ONE-D
skill.description: Drone which flies up above the map to scan for enemy movement at Lion's command. If a Defender moves during this scan, the drone will detect that movement and ping them repeatedly for Attackers to see

skill.name: ADRENAL SURGE
skill.description: Activating Adrenal Surge allows affected allies to gain a permanent boost in health (20 HP), on top of other small benefits.

skill.name: ERC-7
skill.description: Activating the gadget will erase Vigil from video feeds for a set amount of time.

skill.name: LOGIC BOMB
skill.description: This device can upload a virus into the Defenders' phones and cause them to buzz incessantly for 12 seconds or until they reset it manually. If a Defender is killed and Dokkaebi is with the Attackers, she can hack their phones to gain access to their camera feeds.

skill.name: KS79 LIFELINE
skill.description: A double barrel launcher that can launch either impact grenades or concussion grenades.

skill.name: GRZMOT MINE
skill.description: Concussive mines that disorient any who come within range.

skill.name: CANDELA
skill.description: The Candela device releases a cluster of flash charges that can either be anchored on surfaces or thrown out as a grenade.

skill.name: GU MINES
skill.description: If stepped on, Gu mines inject a toxin that injure your opponent and limit their speed.

skill.name: BLACK MIRROR
skill.description: A specialised one-way window that can be deployed on any breachable wall. Depressurising the canister ejects the glass.

skill.name: EYENOX MODEL III
skill.description: A mobile tracking device able to both identify and trail a person’s footprints in real-time.

skill.name: X-KAIROS
skill.description: A 40 mm caliber launcher - fires explosive pellets that can be detonated simultaneously from a distance.

skill.name: YOKAI
skill.description: This drone can fire ultrasonic bursts that disorient all targets in a given perimeter. Yokai also transmits a video feed as a regular camera.

skill.name: SILENT STEP
skill.description: An ability that makes Caveira move as silent as possible at the cost of using sidearm only. In addition to this ability, Caveira is capable of interrogations that can reveal enemy location.

skill.name: TACTICAL CROSSBOW
skill.description: A crossbow with incendiary and smoke rounds.

skill.name: RIFLE SHIELD
skill.description: Equippable rifle shield can protect Blackbeard's head from a couple bullets, allowing a slightly higher survivability rate

skill.name: BLACK EYE
skill.description: Portable sticky cameras that can attach on almost any surface for increased surveillance.

skill.name: SKELETON KEY
skill.description: Under-barrel mounted 12 gauge shotgun with four round capacity, used in tandem with an assault rifle.

skill.name: WELCOME MAT
skill.description: Mechanical traps that can be used to incapacitate enemies.

skill.name: SIGNAL DISRUPTOR
skill.description: Jams communications for remotely detonated gadgets or drones in its range as well as blocks any electronic devices and interference.

skill.name: TACTICAL BREACHING HAMMER
skill.description: Soft-breaching hammer.

skill.name: REMOTE GAS GRENADE
skill.description: Remotely activated gas grenade.

skill.name: EMP GRENADE
skill.description: These grenades disable all electronics that are within its area of effect.

skill.name: BREACHING ROUNDS
skill.description: Fires an explosive Breach Round that burrows into a surface and automatically detonates.

skill.name: ARMOR PANEL
skill.description: Bulletproof reinforced barricades deployable on windows or doors.

skill.name: HEARTBEAT SENSOR
skill.description: Device capable of detecting heartbeat in its active radius through floors and walls.

skill.name: EXOTHERMIC CHARGE
skill.description: Big area hard-breaching device.

skill.name: EXTENDABLE SHIELD
skill.description: Extendable bulletproof shield.

skill.name: SHOCK DRONES
skill.description: The Shock Drones are specialized that can shoot lasers at a target. These drones can take out enemy gadgets from afar and shock enemies.

skill.name: STIM PISTOL
skill.description: Fires a hypodermic shot to revive himself or teammates from a distance. Can also provide a temporary boost.

skill.name: ARMOR PACK
skill.description: These Armor Plates can be picked up and equipped for added damage resistance.

skill.name: ACTIVE DEFENSE SYSTEM
skill.description: This device intercepts any incoming throwable projectiles.

skill.name: SHOCK WIRE
skill.description: Electrifying device that can be attached to reinforced walls, deployable shields and barbed wire.

skill.name: FLASH SHIELD
skill.description: Flashing device mounted on a shield. Allows temporary blinding of anyone standing in front.

skill.name: ELECTRONICS DETECTOR
skill.description: Device allowing detection of electronic devices in its radius.

skill.name: CLUSTER CHARGE
skill.description: APM-6 cluster charge propels a group of explosive cluster grenades through any breachable surface.

skill.name: FLIP SIGHT
skill.description: Sniper sight comes with a Thermal Feedback System which can outline long-range marks even through smoke for easier shooting.

skill.name: SHUMIKHA LAUNCHER
skill.description: Area denial heavy incendiary grenade launcher can bounce multiple times, and their fuse timer only starts after the first bounce, giving them a lot of versatility.

skill.name: ENTRY DENIAL DEVICE
skill.description: C4 charge that may be mounted into windows and door frames.
